Message Queue :

Review    Rating INfo     Message    Rating INfo       Company
System     ---------->    Queue     ------------>      Service


Containerization of microservices :

commands :
./mvnw spring-boot:build-image "-Dspring-boot.build-image.imageName=<your-dockerhub-username>/<your-image-name>"

(example -> ./mvnw spring-boot:build-image "-Dspring-boot.build-image.imageName=arjunbhogavimath/servicereg")


(Note :  "mvnw" is a maven wrapper used to containerize any spring boot application)